THIRD-PARTY NOTICES
===================

This project's demonstration game "Zork1" (the sources under `Sources/Zork1/`)
is an original Swift re-implementation of the interactive-fiction classic
*Zork I: The Great Underground Empire*.

Zork I was written by Marc Blank, Dave Lebling, Bruce Daniels, and Tim Anderson,
and published by Infocom in 1980.


Reproduced textual content
--------------------------

The room descriptions, object descriptions, and player-facing messages in
`Sources/Zork1/` reproduce text from the original Zork I source code. That text
was taken from the publicly available source-code collection published at:

    https://github.com/historicalsource/zork1

